*****************************
======ISING 1D SIMULATOR=====
*****************************

Folder contains
- Code files
	* Monte_Carlo_ISING_1D.cpp  // Simulation code, can be used for Metropolis or Gibbs 
				   // works with data from input file or as arguments
				   // from command line: progressive step for temp.,
				   // total temperature steps, restart command,
				   // measure type command, number of thermalisation steps 
				   // and measure mode.
				   // Needs "random.h" library to compile
	* Monte_Carlo_ISING_1D.h	   // Contains constants and external function definition

- input.dat  			   // Input file that contains all initial data 

- launcher.sh			   // Script that launches in sequence simulation for 
				   // different temperatures; receives number of temps 
				   // between 0.5 and 2 and equilibration number;
				   // passes to programme restart_bool and measure_bool

- clean.sh			   // Removes all txt files and resets final configuration
